title: ‘Fast 9’ and the ‘Fast & Furious’ Rankings
description:
The long-awaited ‘Fast 9’ is here, so Sean and Amanda are digging into the entire ‘Fast & Furious’ series of movies and ranking ’em all with the man who lives his life one-quarter of a pod at a time, Shea Serrano.

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guest: Shea Serrano
Producer: Bobby Wagner
